{# ARG-048 — Midgard tier LaTeX template (Phase-2 jinja2-latex wiring).

   Cycle 5 / ARG-048 swaps the Phase-1 scaffold for a full template that
   mirrors the WeasyPrint HTML layout for the Midgard (CISO brief) tier.

   Render contract — every Jinja2 placeholder MUST be passed through the
   ``latex_escape`` filter (registered by
   :func:`src.reports.pdf_backend.render_latex_template`) when the value
   originates from user-controlled input (tenant ID, scan ID, target,
   AI-generated narrative). Numeric / boolean values from typed schemas
   are safe to render without escaping.

   Block-comment markers ``%~`` are used so the file remains a valid
   LaTeX source even when rendered through a vanilla Jinja2 env (no
   ``%`` line-comments leak inside template logic). #}
